150	93.33	1120.00	1800.00	28	-37.78	40	Data

Note: The Error % is normalized to the Dial reading. Absolute errors are 
much larger numbers.

I used a fish scale to do the calibration.  I checked the fish scale with 
bar bell weights.

With the small wrench I moved a 9.75 lb weight along the lever arm. On the 
med wrench I varied the weight (fish scale) at three fixed points on the 
arm.

Chuck

